blog.name: jamespotterstardis
blog.title: So many fandoms, so little time.
blog.description:
Harry Potter, Ouat, DW, Sherlock, Disney, Avengers, Glee, The Flash, Supernatural, Legends of Tomorrow, Super Girl ...
{Slytherin🐍}

tags: i'm also a fan of bex and bowie
body:
Andi Mack;

On Andi Mack my favourite ships are;

Cyrus and TJ - need I say any more? They’re just fantastic together and really need some more screen time. Their relationship is one of my favourites on Disney because they are generally really good for one another. Cyrus helps TJ see the world less angrily, lets him know it’s okay to have a learning disability and what it’s like to have a real friend. TJ helps Cyrus overcome his fears, is extra support in his life and helps him with his problems.  Cyrus needed a guy friend, so did TJ from what I see he’s got team mates and aquatainces but no real friend, and the Not So Scary Basketball Guy turned up. He even turned up to Cyrus’ Bar Mitzvah! In my head they’re practically married. On a side note I love their nicknames;  Not So Scary Basketball Guy and Underdog. Cyrus smiles this really cute and shy smile when he gets Underdog. My number one ship.

Buffy and Marty - The Slayer and Marty from the party. Even though they’ve only a few eps and scenes I still quite ship them. When they were one upping each other, they were trying to impress each other. Something sparked within their first meeting. {When they were stretching  I’m sure he was checking her out}. The banter between is definitely flirty and they’ve had couple-y moments. Also, when Buffy told Andi that Marty was dating someone she seemed down. They definitely need to meet up again.

Andi and Walker - Now these guys are my second favourite ship. They click much more than Andi and Jonah ever did. With Jonah, she was constantly second guessing herself, blaming herself when things went wrong and they didn’t have much, if anything, in common. “I wanna remember the moment I met you”, who says that to just a friend? They had sparks within the first few seconds of meeting. At Cyrus’ Bar Mitzvah he could’ve drawn Bex and Bowie as well but he focused all of his attention on Andi. She’s eager to know more about him, they video chatted constantly  and when they did hang out he bought her a snack. I believe they had their first day at the gallery, drawing that rainbow and to remember that amazing time Walker gave her those shoes. Choosing between Walker and Jonah Andi was choosing between following her head or heart. She chose her head, Jonah, because I think because she had fancied him for a while it was the logical choice against someone she’d just met. Andi still likes him but now has to hide it due to Walker being with her best friend. She’s not really okay with it.

{I also love Bex and Bowie♡♡}

ooo interesting mix up…

I’d have to go, Bowie, because he’s a puppy and i love how he just,, came into this crazy new life and accepted it full on, no looking back

Then Jonah cos ugh my heart this boy has stuff and WE NEED TO SEE IT

Then Andi cos girl be dealing with a lot of bs and she’s pushing through still being adorable and trying to make good in her life

Then Cece that character development coming through and i stan her pettiness 

and Marty is last cos,, lets face it, he’s just a white boy that can run fast and has a cute crush

summary: So I’ve been watching since season 1 but I haven’t used my tumblr in ages and I may or may not have been dying from Tyrus lately...
caption:
So I’ve been watching since season 1 but I haven’t used my tumblr in ages and I may or may not have been dying from Tyrus lately and made a sideblog just so I could scream about it.

Anyway I’m not good at edits but I just really like this song with Tyrus so I tried my best to make a little something. I just like how Cyrus and T.J. seem to lift each other up when they need it and believe in each other even when other people don’t. Also I’m not trying to throw shade at Buffy cause I love her and also TJ and Buffy being good friends as the show progresses. It’s just more so a comparison of how other ppl see TJ vs. how Cyrus see’s TJ and vice versa.
